ygData.messageBody:
<smiles> yes, it sure does! But more importantly - all songs are like fine
wine and get lots better with age. So knowing that, I suggest you choose
your early songs first - unless you need a newer one for a specific purpose
- they will be stronger.

Sylly Songsynger
<Spirit of the Moon>
Bard of the 35th song
somewhere on Innoruuk
